(numRobEntries, area_cell_area).explanation: Increasing ROB entries requires more storage cells and associated logic, directly increasing the physical cell area needed for implementation;

(numRobEntries, power_register).explanation: More ROB entries mean more register storage elements that consume power through switching activity and leakage, directly increasing register power consumption;
